" Operations for quotes, parenthesis
" Use `cs"'` to replace `"`" by `'`, or `cs"<p>` for tags
" Use `ds(` to delete parenthesis, etc.
Plug 'tpope/vim-surround'

" Omni complete w/ tab
" Simply use `<Tab>` to autocomplete
